lead_paragraph: PSV Eindhoven's hopes of reaching the Champions League knockout stages hinge on beating mighty Bayern Munich on Tuesday, said coach Phillip Cocu as he called on his team to believe success was possible.

headline.print_headline: PSV Champions League Bid Hinges on Beating Bayern-Cocu
